quote.summary: China Kangda Food Co Ltd is an investment holding company primarily engaged in the food manufacturing and processing. The Company operates its business through four segments. The Processed Foods segment is engaged in the production, processing, sale and distribution of processed foods which include instant soup, curry food, chicken-based cooked products, roasted rabbit food, meatballs, de-oxygenated consumer packed chestnuts, seafood and other products. The Chilled and Frozen Rabbit Meat segment is engaged in the production, processing, sale and distribution of chilled and frozen rabbit meat. The Chilled and Frozen Chicken Meat segment is engaged in the production, processing, sale and distribution of chilled and frozen chicken meat. The Other Products segment is engaged in the production, processing, sale and distribution of other products which include chicken and rabbit meat by products and pet food products. The Company conducts its business in the domestic and overseas markets.
